title: Nanda's
typeOfFood: Vegan, Italian, Organic, Western, Fast food, Bakery
description: Vegan restaurant in the city centre. Serves burgers, hot dogs, sweets, and in-house baked goods. Uses only organic whole grain flours for sandwiches, and organic fair-trade beverages and coffee. Entirely low-consumption designed with LED lights and all crockery and packaging is compostable.
